---
import Minimal from "../layouts/Minimal.astro";
---

<Minimal>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-4 border-primary my-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-content text-center mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 text-center mb-10">
      Your privacy is important to us. We are committed to protecting your personal data and being transparent about how we use it.
    </p>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-content mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          We only ask for personal information when itâ€™s essential to provide you with our services. 
          We collect data fairly and lawfully, with your knowledge and consent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-content mb-2">How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          We retain collected information only for as long as necessary. We safeguard your data 
          using industry-standard security measures to prevent unauthorized access or misuse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-content mb-2">Sharing Information</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          Your personal data is never shared publicly or with third parties, except when required by law.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-content mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          You have the right to refuse providing personal information, though this may affect service availability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-content mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-400">
          If you have any questions about how we handle user data, please reach out to us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">
      This policy is effective as of <span class="text-primary">[Date]</span>.
    </p>
  </main>
</Minimal>
